{"tid":1751983,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求 缺一不可 你還記得嗎？","createTime":"2019-11-24T18:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T18:56:37.000Z","uid":239516,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"38f736b3e52bfb238536d8c971b9fdd4665f052b","tid":1751983,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:36:43.000Z","msg":"區議會早就要贏 本來就屬於該區市民<br />\n香港人醒了 識得簡單踏出一步去投票 <br />\n我地成個民主運動 流左咁多血、汗、淚就只係換來區議會既勝利？<br />\n唔夠 唔夠 唔夠 我地只係拎返原來屬於我哋嘅野<br />\n有咩值得高興？<br />\n你可以有短暫既快樂 但你依然要保持憤怒<br />\n615 第一位義士死去 <br />\n被毆打 被強姦 被槍殺 被自殺<br />\n直至依家黑警攻入大學 <br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得我地贏左<br />\n我寧願我地區議會大敗！<br />\n<br />\n我既怨恨、憤怒、悲傷一直都係到<br />\n直至五大訴求達成<br />\n公義得到彰顯 光復香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 保持憤怒</span></span>"},{"pid":"259f9a22ab210ea673225df97e84dc94fe18e011","tid":1751983,"uid":283686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:37:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b7db15c70d024e7b1f07ac727e756da79c409cb8","tid":1751983,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:38:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 保持憤怒</span></span>"},{"pid":"251fc37ea82a337fbf420840c266635a126d9293","tid":1751983,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:39:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"24db67ebe2194a88f39a80bd5331c66ba202911e","tid":1751983,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:39:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"955bfee64e0a7c08d4eeb0db06e217f94754707c","tid":1751983,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:39:33.00